WEBVTT

00:00.899 --> 00:03.967
Splitting a word into chunks can improve your spelling.

00:06.216 --> 00:10.163
Mend can be split into men - d.

00:15.331 --> 00:19.085
Flag can be split into fl - ag.

00:20.807 --> 00:24.385
Longer words can be split into chunks called syllables.

00:26.244 --> 00:27.998
Each syllable makes a beat.

00:28.491 --> 00:30.867
Hold your hand under your chin and say the word.

00:31.375 --> 00:34.158
Each time your mouth opens, the word has a syllable.

00:35.720 --> 00:38.457
Un - der - stand - ing.

00:39.088 --> 00:39.977
Understanding.

